title: Hour 1 - Steph Curry MVP Performance, LIV Tour Lacking
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Steph Curry MVP Performance, LIV Tour Lacking
description:
Dan finally gets a chance to react to Warriors PG Steph Curry's dominant NBA Finals performance in game 4 on Friday, and was underwhelmed by the inaugural LIV golf tournament.
